sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant App as BaseConverterApp
    participant Tab as Notebook Tab
    participant Base as Base Converter
    participant Int as Integer Visualizer
    participant Flt as Float Visualizer
    participant Worker as Float Worker Thread
    participant Half as Half Panel
    participant Single as Single Panel
    participant Double as Double Panel

    User->>App: Ctrl+1 / Ctrl+2 / Ctrl+3
    App->>Tab: _select_tab(index)

    alt Base Converter active
        User->>Base: Edit binary/decimal/hex entry
        Base->>App: StringVar trace
        App->>App: _update_from_source(source)
        App->>App: parse_value + format_value
        App->>Base: Update other fields + panel columns
        App->>Base: Push history + status
    else Integer Visualizer active
        User->>Int: Edit decimal input / type
        Int->>Int: parse_decimal_input
        Int->>Int: int_wrap_and_flags + int_bits
        Int->>Int: Render bit boxes, signed/unsigned views
        Int->>Int: Highlight wrapped result on overflow
    else Float Visualizer active
        User->>Flt: Edit shared decimal input
        Flt->>Flt: parse + debounce(30ms) + request_id++
        Flt->>Worker: build_all_float_panel_display_data(value)
        Worker-->>Flt: panel display data (async)
        alt stale request_id
            Flt->>Flt: drop result
            Flt->>Flt: print stale timing to stdout
        else latest request_id
            Flt->>Half: apply_display_data(...)
            Flt->>Single: apply_display_data(...)
            Flt->>Double: apply_display_data(...)
            Flt->>Flt: update sign/exponent/mantissa fields
            Flt->>Flt: print debounce/compute/queue/apply/total ms
        end
        User->>Flt: Edit float panel sign/exponent/mantissa fields
        Flt->>Flt: decode source format bit fields
        Flt->>Flt: synchronize decimal + half + single + double
    end
